{"tid":1362322,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[728元朗之後] 燈柱 & 社會信用系統","createTime":"2019-07-25T00:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T14:06:24.000Z","uid":12929,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2d968b003b7e64f9585e9da595d815beb4255d8","tid":1362322,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:08:29.000Z","msg":"香港人要贏就要夠多人，首先要出師有名，打嘅旗號要係香港大眾都有共鳴嘅標題。而家有嘅係<br />\n- 五大訴求<br />\n- 警黑勾結<br />\n- 上環違規開鎗<br />\n- 燈柱 &amp; 社會信用系統<br />\n<br />\n攪地鐵一齊罷工當然可以，唔好攪著屋企就得。將心比己，你係黃絲但住緊嘅地方有藍絲攪事，整有人黎光復攪到你雞毛鴨血，無網上，無水電煤。你會點諗？<br />\n<br />\n結論: 我地要鎗口對反政府、黑警。衝擊公共資源係可以，但係破壞社區安定就萬萬唔可以做。721元朗係好好嘅例子，好在出手嘅係政府、係中共、係黑警先沒有令民意逆轉。<br />\n假若星期六嘅行動係牽涉圍村大眾嘅祠堂（包括斷水、斷網、斷電等等），咁我地將要準備有一群支持者轉邊支持政府出手鎮壓。這是Not In My Back Yard (NIMBYS) 嘅心理反認。<br />\n<br />\n另外香港人面對緊嘅仲有 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">燈柱 &amp; 社會信用系統</span></span> ，要係民意失速之前拆毀所有監控硬件，要係政府完成硬件設置前拆晒佢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67543057_2301274246761916_8883699518843912192_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQkfK4sLH9Wqi9HJfEiOmt2zr0uWezbHYXoZYoZHs2HNRMkTHB8oeydtmjxrmyAwGe4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=2de90c12af61b90302cde13c7b9de391&amp;oe=5D9FD445\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67543057_2301274246761916_8883699518843912192_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQkfK4sLH9Wqi9HJfEiOmt2zr0uWezbHYXoZYoZHs2HNRMkTHB8oeydtmjxrmyAwGe4%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D2de90c12af61b90302cde13c7b9de391%26oe%3D5D9FD445&h=379b0293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67269822_10162223590700691_2140269644835979264_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQnVmkKAXRYfeiWJ1tkyQQL6ElosHXkQJdIXqwZ7O6hVXz7TbULUtC_d9gPO2LH1ExI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=35d4390caa859c0f4c83f0d4f18d2240&amp;oe=5DB3B460\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67269822_10162223590700691_2140269644835979264_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQnVmkKAXRYfeiWJ1tkyQQL6ElosHXkQJdIXqwZ7O6hVXz7TbULUtC_d9gPO2LH1ExI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D35d4390caa859c0f4c83f0d4f18d2240%26oe%3D5DB3B460&h=0f365d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67260195_2297408867148454_2791389100681199616_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_oc=AQliR-xoYByPnlDm87jTt-Jz3AIRm3qXOxhN4VF6-TMfkKgGOkq1iCk9z3IdQs3nlRE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=cbab1c81a7c9a24f4774f89997b68713&amp;oe=5DA9A7FC\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67260195_2297408867148454_2791389100681199616_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_oc%3DAQliR-xoYByPnlDm87jTt-Jz3AIRm3qXOxhN4VF6-TMfkKgGOkq1iCk9z3IdQs3nlRE%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Dcbab1c81a7c9a24f4774f89997b68713%26oe%3D5DA9A7FC&h=95c980e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AntiCCTV/photos/a.2295533484002659/2301274243428583/?type=3&amp;permPage=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAntiCCTV%2Fphotos%2Fa.2295533484002659%2F2301274243428583%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26permPage%3D1&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D6EbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=d39bca9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AntiCCTV/photos/a.2295533484002659/2301274243428583/?type=3&amp;permPage=1</a>"},{"pid":"2f96df5662c4d828545f016a3e85f00b26e92f58","tid":1362322,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:11:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"fbab9bf361cee4e5a6612f12ecd2c9139518e927","tid":1362322,"uid":278667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:28:33.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"7fb4d889330ccc4290a0663d538379cf56d52890","tid":1362322,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:12:34.000Z","